bilingual.source: Later he got work on a boat.
bilingual.target: 后来他在船上找到工作。
后来那个男孩和阿迪尔说话了。

bilingual.source: Later on, they heard a noise again.
bilingual.target: 后来，他们又听到了一阵响声。
这家人后来获得了英国国籍。

bilingual.source: The ex-football star later turned to acting.
bilingual.target: 这位前足球明星后来转行做演员。

bilingual.source: Later Helen learnt to read, write and speak.
bilingual.target: 后来海伦学会了读书、写字和说话。

bilingual.source: He taught in London and later returned to China.
bilingual.target: 他在伦敦教书，后来回到了中国。

bilingual.source: Jane wonders how the girl became a doctor later.
bilingual.target: 简想知道那个女孩后来是怎么成为医生的。

bilingual.source: Later, Winton received various honours for his achievement.
bilingual.target: 后来，温顿因其成就获得了各种荣誉。

bilingual.source: She trained hard, so she became a great player later.
bilingual.target: 她刻苦训练，所以后来成为了一名优秀的运动员。

list.abstract: 《Later》是一部由刘玉玲主演的电视剧。
英伦绝美浩室音乐厂牌Seamless旗下《Later》系列，继上集请到弛放电音名团Bent后，这次荣邀来自大不列颠的兄弟档二人组Faze Action共同主理。

yingyinNormal.en: And later, this truck comes to haul him off.
yingyinNormal.zh: 后来这辆卡车把他载走。

yingyinNormal.en: And he saved me, taught me lessons that I later shared with your father.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是他救了我，教会我东西，后来我分享给了你父亲。

yingyinNormal.en: This custom was later appropriated by Northern Europeans and eventually it becomes the so-called Christmas tree.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这种风俗后来被北欧人继承，于是演变成了现在的圣诞树。

yingyinNormal.en: So later, he calls me into his office and tells me that he'll have to let me go, because I'm not a team player.
yingyinNormal.zh: 后来他把我叫到他的办公室，告诉我他要解雇我因为我不合群。

yingyinNormal.en: Later that day we found out we blocked the water all right. We sent it upstream. The whole Lang farm washed away.
yingyinNormal.zh: 后来我们发现，我们挡住了洪水，洪水回流，朗家的整个农场都被冲没了。

yingyinNormal.en: Then she taught her daughter to make shoes. And later, she taught her son-in-law. Then her Grand kids got roped in.
yingyinNormal.zh: 然后她教会了她女儿怎么做鞋子，接着，她教会了她女婿，后来她的孙辈也进入了这个行当。

yingyinNormal.en: And I'd planned for music later on. And maybe a bit of a hoolie. None of which would be suitable in the Great Hall.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我还打算稍后来点音乐，大家玩玩闹闹，但这些都不适合在大厅做。

yingyinNormal.en: Ask Again Later. Later is not good enough.
yingyinNormal.zh: 待会再问，这个答案不够好。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, we'll talk later, Mater.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，我们晚点再聊，脱线

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, I'll see you guys later.
yingyinNormal.zh: 待会儿见。

yingyinNormal.en: All right, I'll see you later.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好了，回见。

yingyinNormal.en: I want a later curfew too. Why?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我也想晚点回家。为啥？

yingyinNormal.en: Mom, I'll call you later. Yeah.
yingyinNormal.zh: 妈，我再回电给你，是的。

yingyinNormal.en: Right, I'll see you guys later.
yingyinNormal.zh: 回头见了。

yingyinNormal.en: Two weeks later, I left Vietnam.
yingyinNormal.zh: 两星期后，我离开越南。

yingyinNormal.en: Bye bye ,see you later. Bye bye Mummy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 再见，一会见了。再见，妈妈。

yingyinNormal.en: You know what? Let's, let's talk later.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你知道吗？我们待会再谈。

yingyinNormal.en: But then, later that night... Yeah, baby.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但那晚的晚些时候…好啊，宝贝。

yingyinNormal.en: Bye Rach. Bye. I'll call you later. Bye Ross.
yingyinNormal.zh: 再见瑞秋。再见。我再打给你。好，再见。罗斯再见。

yingyinNormal.en: Aren't I seeing you later? We are good to go.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不是应该过会儿见你吗？我们万事俱备了。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Rise of the Planet of the Apes》

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Both apps, however, were <highlight>later</highlight> scrapped, after Microsoft said it had used their best features in its own products.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，这两个应用程序后来都被废弃了，因为微软表示，它已经在自己的产品中使用了它们最好的功能。

examination_example.sentence: Little more than a decade <highlight>later</highlight>, the share of imports was 25.8 percent.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 十多年后，进口份额为25.8%。

examination_example.sentence: Hill's pressure <highlight>later</highlight> led to the creation of national parks and green belts.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 希尔的压力后来导致了国家公园和绿化带的建立。

sense_info_list.zh: 接近末期的; 晚年的

examination_example.sentence: Even more surprising is that more than half of "unretirees" said they would be employed in their <highlight>later</highlight> years.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 更令人惊讶的是，超过一半的“未退休者”表示他们将在晚年继续就业。

examination_example.sentence: Many people are preparing to do so because they are worried about making ends meet in their <highlight>later</highlight> years.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 许多人都准备这样做，因为他们担心晚年入不敷出。

examination_example.sentence: However, the mechanisms proposed were unwieldy and the Bill was voted down following the change in government <highlight>later</highlight> that year.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，提议的机制是非常拙劣的，该法案在那年年末政府换届后被否决。

sense_info_list.zh: (用于告别的)再见; 回头见

word_usage.usage: later作形容词时，无比较级和最高级形式，只用于名词之前，修饰该名词，如；a later chapter

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全四级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Three days <highlight>later</highlight>, the happy wife called to claim the ring.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 三天后，幸福的妻子打电话来认领戒指。

examination_example.sentence: She tried to give him money <highlight>later</highlight> on, but he graciously declined.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 她后来试图给他钱，但他婉言谢绝了。

examination_example.sentence: Although frozen dinners were invented in the 40s, their popularity didn't boom until televisions became popular a decade or so <highlight>later</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 虽然冷冻食品是在40年代发明的，但直到大约十年后电视开始流行，冷冻食品才开始普及开来。

sense_info_list.zh: 接近末期的; 晚年的

examination_example.sentence: Creme wanted to show to <highlight>later</highlight> generations that French chefs of his time were most outstanding in the world.
examination_example.sentence_trans: Creme想向后人展示，他那个时代的法国厨师是世界上最杰出的。

examination_example.sentence: Most people's minds function at a high level even in their <highlight>later</highlight> years, according to researcher Timothy Salthouse.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 研究人员蒂莫西·索尔特豪斯表示，即使到了晚年，大多数人的思维能力仍处于较高水平。

examination_example.sentence: They tend to decline in people's <highlight>later</highlight> years.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们往往在人们的晚年衰落。

sense_info_list.zh: (sooner or later)迟早; 早晚有一天

examination_example.sentence: It will become the norm sooner or <highlight>later</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这迟早会成为常态。

examination_example.sentence: They may be exhausted sooner or <highlight>later</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们迟早会筋疲力尽。

sense_info_list.zh: (用于告别的)再见; 回头见

examination_example.sentence: Fine, see you <highlight>later</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 好的，回头见！

direction_info.description:
数据源自2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2015-2022年全国卷高考试卷，包括阅读、完形、单选、填空、听力、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Anneke said, and she wants others <highlight>later</highlight> in their lives to catch up with her on this journey.
examination_example.sentence_trans: Anneke说，她希望其他人在以后的生活中能在这段旅程中赶上她。

examination_example.sentence: A few minutes <highlight>later</highlight>, when I landed the trick, my friends beat their boards loud, shouting: "Safe! Safe! Safe!"
examination_example.sentence_trans: 几分钟后，当我完成这个动作时，我的朋友们大声拍打他们的滑板，喊道，“酷！酷！酷！”

examination_example.sentence: Two years <highlight>later</highlight> I got my diploma.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 两年后我拿到了文凭。

examination_example.sentence: Encouraging children to express themselves in constructive ways could help to form healthy emotional responses in <highlight>later</highlight> life.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 鼓励孩子们以建设性的方式表达自己，有助于在以后的生活中形成健康的情绪反应。

examination_example.sentence: The qualities carry over to <highlight>later</highlight> years and make you better able to relate and connect with others.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这些品质会延续到以后的岁月，让你能更好地与他人相处和联系。

examination_example.sentence: They hope could help them to continue driving into <highlight>later</highlight> life.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们希望能帮助他们在以后的生活中继续开车。

direction_info.description:

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: A week <highlight>later</highlight>  Mike got the photos.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一周后，迈克拿到了照片。

examination_example.sentence: Only seconds <highlight>later</highlight>, Mary was inside the secret garden.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 仅仅几秒钟后，玛丽就进入了秘密花园。

examination_example.sentence: Years <highlight>later</highlight>, the tree had grown tall.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 多年后，这棵树长高了。
